             watched the prisoner, from his information I stopped the men when they were leaving work, I searched the prisoner and found near a whole skin of morrocco leather in a handkerchief in his coat pocket, it is worth seven shillings. The prisoner said he took it to make some braces. This is the morrocco skin, it is Mr. Maberley's property.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I leave it to the mercy of the court.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called four witnesses, who gave him a good character.</p>

